{"tid":882031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"退休導盲犬與訓練員隔6年重逢 彼此還認得嗎？","createTime":"2018-10-30T01:48:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T02:08:49.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6c8c74694dafbb5e0d23893ba2041cda5e6528ce","tid":882031,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:48:01.000Z","msg":"導盲犬完成短短4個月的訓練後就會與訓練員道別，與有需要的視障人士展開新生活，基本上日後都不會再見到訓練員。日本節目特別安排剛退休的導盲犬與訓練員重聚，看到6年沒見的熟悉臉孔，狗狗會有甚麼反應呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1956933/org/7f68e6506fbac5380fa18627a067ef6e.png/lmzbfYmRIm1yL51ndQQCm0GDQDCQhVkHv_kk6r_5JOo?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1956933%2Forg%2F7f68e6506fbac5380fa18627a067ef6e.png%2FlmzbfYmRIm1yL51ndQQCm0GDQDCQhVkHv_kk6r_5JOo%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=e34897ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Nana（中間）是橫山小姐新人時期訓練出來的導盲犬。（節目截圖）</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本導盲犬的一生<br />\n<br />\n一般來說，有義工家庭會選擇讓狗狗的孩子成為導盲犬，出生後兩個月會到另一義工家庭生活，學習人類社會相關的知識及習慣。一歲時就會開始為期4個月的導盲犬訓練，能成功通過考核的話，就能]會正式成為導盲犬；沒通過考核（例如會暈車），便會當作寵物犬供人領養。<br />\n<br />\n導盲犬平均會在8至12歲時退休，作為寵物犬被領養後展開新生活安度餘生。因此一與訓練員分別後，基本上不會再見面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1957013/org/52b75e0d3481547300ab8513a33e19cf.png/JLFDmfQWZXLjFowCtMW7wLFSgQMwr6CO_5HTV_-R01c?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1957013%2Forg%2F52b75e0d3481547300ab8513a33e19cf.png%2FJLFDmfQWZXLjFowCtMW7wLFSgQMwr6CO_5HTV_-R01c%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=f83982ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Nana剛出生時的照片。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一別永隔的訓練員與導盲犬<br />\n<br />\nNana是橫山小姐剛剛成為訓練員時所訓練出來的導盲犬。對橫山小姐來說，Nana非常特別，她亦花盡心思訓練牠。遺憾的是，當成功成為導盲犬的Nana與橫山小姐道別時，Nana沒有回頭看過橫山小姐一眼。<br />\n<br />\n橫山小姐對此表示有點不開心，但也代表Nana能盡快忘記她，全心全意展開新生活，以訓練員的角度出發，這是最好不過的結果......<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1957093/org/33bd8b3a170fbe366b7cd97dcf5bab35.png/8oTnOlMuFxcrT77W9TK6iviMCOVS-CK-K89fQCvPX0A?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1957093%2Forg%2F33bd8b3a170fbe366b7cd97dcf5bab35.png%2F8oTnOlMuFxcrT77W9TK6iviMCOVS-CK-K89fQCvPX0A%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=234a3190&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">橫山小姐與Nana(右)再會的一刻（節目截圖）</span><br />\n<br />\n闊別6年的重逢<br />\n<br />\n日本節目《ソノサキ》為安排橫山小姐與Nana再度相見，特別探訪Nana的新主人石原小姐。石原小姐亦很爽快地答應讓他們重聚，到底Nana記不記得橫山小姐呢？<br />\n<br />\n訓練員與退休導盲犬重逢片段<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%AF%B5%E7%89%A9/245284/%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E5%B0%8E%E7%9B%B2%E7%8A%AC%E8%88%87%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E5%93%A1%E9%9A%946%E5%B9%B4%E9%87%8D%E9%80%A2-%E5%A0%B4%E9%9D%A2%E8%B6%85%E6%84%9F%E5%8B%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25AF%25B5%25E7%2589%25A9%2F245284%2F%25E9%2580%2580%25E4%25BC%2591%25E5%25B0%258E%25E7%259B%25B2%25E7%258A%25AC%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%25A8%2593%25E7%25B7%25B4%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%259A%25946%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E9%2580%25A2-%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%259D%25A2%25E8%25B6%2585%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%258B%2595&d=UgOTwj4WJrJn7233pRlQ3S7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=9819396c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%AF%B5%E7%89%A9/245284/%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E5%B0%8E%E7%9B%B2%E7%8A%AC%E8%88%87%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E5%93%A1%E9%9A%946%E5%B9%B4%E9%87%8D%E9%80%A2-%E5%A0%B4%E9%9D%A2%E8%B6%85%E6%84%9F%E5%8B%95</a>"},{"pid":"96a7c05806eaae8fe1b6aa3715409684154c7bb2","tid":882031,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:53:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">孔雀大師=死雞大師</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br /